{"tid":734267,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登都應該要「撐Thanos」","createTime":"2018-07-08T13:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T13:44:50.000Z","uid":90808,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1cb7440b0715d553cbd26990c136f938a5dabe02","tid":734267,"uid":90808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T13:11:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/07/08/thanos-subreddit-ban-half-online-fan-communities/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2Fthanos-subreddit-ban-half-online-fan-communities%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=Fmtq7n1FPToUltkVEwSsesmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=7d326980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/07/08/thanos-subreddit-ban-half-online-fan-communities/fun-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\nReddit 「撐 Thanos」討論區貫徹宗旨 隨機封鎖一半成員<br />\n<br />\n在上一集《復仇者聯盟》電影中，反派 Thanos 認爲要維持宇宙平衡必須消滅一半的人口，而在現實中有不少的影迷都認爲他的理論正確，在 Reddit 上的相關討論區，更決定把這個理念貫徹實行，隨機把一半的成員封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n在 Reddit 上支持 Thanos 理論的 Sub-Reddit「Thanos Did Nothing Wrong」上，發起了一個行動，爲了保持討論區的平衡，根據 Thanos 的宗旨將會把其 352,000 名成員隨機挑選出一半封鎖，這個封鎖行動將會在明天進行。其實在前幾天他們決定這個行動的時候，討論區的成員只有約 120,000 人，不過由於這個行動太過有趣，讓更多人加入自願被封鎖，成員的數量也因此增加。<br />\n<br />\n由於今次封鎖行動的規模龐大，管理員要向 Reddit 方面取得批准才可以做出大規模封鎖，Reddit 方面已經同意並提供了技術支援。面對可能會被消失於討論區之中，不少成員都感到相當興奮，看來他們確實是真心支持 Thanos。<br />\n<br />\n來源：Reddit"},{"pid":"3dde9289e902a18cd848351aed8b0af0f3c710ce","tid":734267,"uid":104171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T13:17:26.000Z","msg":"自願被封<br />\n姐係有幾個分身啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b2eb19eeaba5315ed497780a4b4db016836f43","tid":734267,"uid":61515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T13:31:58.000Z","msg":"簡單D咪開多2個區 隨機一半人只可以入其中一個區 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca1725c5e402ced6c6e18ed5ac1f15a662c5a21","tid":734267,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T13:4